Edo State – popular Nigerian Instagram comedian, has added to his mother’s joy by building a house for her in Edo State. Sharing a video of the apartment they used to stay in, Gbovo disclosed that he built the house for his mother from money he made from comedy. He wrote: “This is what some people kill people to ACHIEVE, but i ACHIEVED mine by putting smiles on peoples faces.“A gift to my mum @nenegold_” Below is the video he shared to celebrate on Instagram. Congratulations To Me On My New House 🏠 Specially dedicated to My Lovely Mom @nenegold_ #JoyAtLast #NaMoneyGoShame A post shared by  Osaigbovo Endurance (@comediangbovo) on Nov 4, 2019 at 12:27am PST Source